<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>华泰柏瑞新金融地产业绩表现</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201105/b9820cf373cb435a9f8a65017417a91a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
